Random Potion: 
---------------
Title: Philter
Effect: Intimidation. Gives the user a huge booming voice that terrifies those around.
Strength: Temporary but strong and wears off quickly.
Side Effect: Weakness to physical damage.
Container: A large metal bottle.
Colour: White.
Appearance: Steam coming from it.
Texture: Slimey.
Taste: Egg.
Label: Its description in draconic.
Duration: 1 month
Curability: Apprentice Level (Second Easiest)
